      "created": "2026-04-03T19:17:33.000Z",
      "modified": "2026-04-03T19:17:33.000Z",
      "name": "TwizAdmin CryptoGuard Stealer",
      "description": "Python-based multi-chain crypto clipper and infostealer (v1.21). Monitors clipboard for cryptocurrency addresses across 8 chains and substitutes with attacker wallets. Also exfiltrates browser cookies, Discord tokens, Telegram sessions, Steam/Minecraft credentials, and screenshots.",
