      "modified": "2026-04-03T19:17:33.000Z",
      "name": "TwizAdmin SeedFinder Scanner",
      "description": "BIP-39 seed phrase scanner (v2.2_ULTRA_STRICT). Scans all local files for cryptocurrency seed phrases and uploads matches with file contents to C2.",
