      "modified": "2026-04-03T19:17:33.000Z",
      "name": "crpx0 Ransomware",
      "description": "Python-based ransomware using Fernet (AES-128-CBC) encryption. Adds .crpx0 extension. Drops ransom notes in English, Russian, and Chinese. Operated under the DataBreachPlus identity. Targets documents, media, databases, code, and engineering files.",
      "malware_types": [
        "ransomware"
      ],
